data.text:
Contents: States and Counties

The population of the states and counties of South Sudan according to the last census and latest official projections.

Presidential decrees of 2015 and 2017 replace the ten states by 32 new states.

The icon links to further information about a selected division including its population structure (gender, age groups, age distribution).
